commit.message:
libgcc2.h (exception_descriptor): Don't forward-declare.

2007-04-02  Dave Korn  <dave.korn@artimi.com>

	* libgcc2.h (exception_descriptor):  Don't forward-declare.
	(__get_eh_table_language, __get_eh_table_version):  Delete
	prototypes of long-dead functions.
